## 1️⃣ Daemon Architecture

### Quy trình khởi động

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as XXTExplorer (UI)
    participant Tweak as 1feaks.dylib
    participant Daemon as ReportCrash (Daemon)
    participant UI as XXTUIService (Hidden App)
    
    App->>Tweak: App launch trigger
    Tweak->>Tweak: posix_spawn() / launchd plist
    Tweak->>Daemon: Start ReportCrash process
    Daemon->>Daemon: Load libxxtouch.so
    Daemon->>Daemon: Init JSC engine + WebRTC
    Daemon->>UI: Launch XXTUIService (hidden)
    UI->>UI: Overlay windows (toast, alerts)
    Tweak-->>App: "daemon connected"
```

### Chi tiết kỹ thuật

| Aspect | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Daemon binary** | `ReportCrash` — đặt tên giống Apple crash reporter để tránh phát hiện |
| **Install path** | `/usr/bin/1ferver/ReportCrash` |
| **LaunchDaemon** | `/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.1func.xxtouch.plist` |
| **Process spawn** | `posix_spawn()` — không dùng `fork()` |
| **Injection** | `opainject` — inject `1feaks.dylib` vào target process |
| **Restart** | `killall -9 ReportCrash` rồi restart qua launchd |
| **Config file** | `/var/mobile/Media/1ferver/1ferver.conf` |
| **Data directory** | `/var/mobile/Media/1ferver/` |

### XXTUIService — Hidden Daemon App

```
NSPrincipalClass: XXTDaemonApp
SBAppTags: [hidden]                    ← Ẩn khỏi SpringBoard
UIApplicationShowsViewsWhileLocked: true  ← Hiển thị khi khóa màn hình
UIApplicationSystemWindowsSecureKey: true  ← Secure window content
```

Đây là app ẩn chạy song song, chịu trách nhiệm hiển thị overlay UI (toast windows, web views) trên top mọi app khác.

### 1feaks.dylib — System Integration Layer

Liên kết **private frameworks**:
- `BackBoardServices` — quản lý backboard session, process lifecycle
- `SpringBoardServices` — `SBSLaunchApplicationWithIdentifier`, `SBLockScreenManager`
- `GraphicsServices` — GSEvent, display management
- `IOKit` — hardware access, `IOHIDEvent*`
- `libMobileGestalt` — device identifier queries
- `JavaScriptCore` — JSC bridge cho Lua↔JS
- `libffi` — foreign function interface cho dynamic calls

Chức năng chính:
- `BKSTerminateApplicationForReasonAndReportWithDescription` — kill app
- `_accessibilityFrontMostApplication` — detect foreground app
- `_frontMostAppOrientation` — detect screen orientation
- `_AXSAssistiveTouchSetEnabled` — toggle AssistiveTouch
- `_recentDisplayIdentifiers` — app switcher history
- `CFRunLoopObserver*` — event loop monitoring
- `DISPATCH_SOURCE_TYPE_MACH_RECV/SEND` — Mach IPC
- `DISPATCH_PROC_FORK/EXEC` — process lifecycle monitoring

