## 2️⃣ WebRTC Live Screen Streaming & Control

### Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "iPhone (Daemon)"
        A["IOSurfaceAccelerator<br/>Screen Capture"] --> B["RTCCVPixelBuffer<br/>Frame Conversion"]
        B --> C["RTCVideoEncoderH264<br/>Hardware Encode"]
        C --> D["RTCPeerConnection<br/>WebRTC Transport"]
        E["CADisplayLink<br/>Frame Timer"] --> A
    end
    
    subgraph "Signaling"
        F["JSCWebSocketServer<br/>(Built-in WS Server)"]
        G["SRWebSocket<br/>(Client WS)"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Browser (Web IDE)"
        H["RTCPeerConnection<br/>Receive Stream"]
        H --> I["Video Element<br/>Live Display"]
        I --> J["Touch Events<br/>→ WebSocket"]
    end
    
    D <-->|"SRTP/DTLS"| H
    F <-->|"SDP Offer/Answer<br/>ICE Candidates"| G
    J -->|"Coordinates"| F
```

### Screen Capture Pipeline

| Stage | Technology | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| **Capture** | `IOSurfaceAccelerator` | Capture system framebuffer — **không phải** chỉ app window |
| **Frame timing** | `CADisplayLink` (`RTCDisplayLinkTimer`) | Sync với display refresh rate |
| **Pixel buffer** | `RTCCVPixelBuffer` ← `CVPixelBuffer` | Zero-copy pixel buffer from IOSurface |
| **Encoding** | `RTCVideoEncoderH264` (VideoToolbox) | Hardware H264 encoding — rất nhanh, ít CPU |
| **Transport** | `RTCPeerConnection` + SRTP/DTLS | P2P encrypted streaming |
| **Decoding** | `RTCVideoDecoderH264` (browser) | Hardware decode ở client |

### Signaling & WebSocket

- **Server**: `JSCWebSocketServer` — WebSocket server chạy ngay trong daemon
- **Client**: `SRWebSocket` (SocketRocket) — mature WebSocket library
- **Protocol**: SDP Offer/Answer exchange + ICE candidate trickle
- **Features**: `addTrack`, `addTransceiverOfType`, `removeTrack`, `startRtcEventLog`

### JavaScript API (trong libxxtouch.so)

```javascript
// Screen module (embedded JS trong binary)
screen.init(orient)        // Set orientation (0-3)
screen.keep()              // Capture và giữ frame hiện tại
screen.unkeep()            // Giải phóng frame
screen.image(l,t,r,b)     // Crop vùng từ kept frame
screen.orientation()       // Get current orientation
screen.is_colors(...)      // Match nhiều color cùng lúc
screen.is_color(...)       // Alias cho is_colors
screen.ocr_text(l,t,r,b,opts,binopt)  // OCR vùng chọn

// Native methods exposed:
screen.captureCanvas()     // Async capture
screen.captureCanvasSync() // Sync capture  
screen.size()              // Get screen dimensions
```

