## 3️⃣ Touch / Tap Simulation

### IOHIDEvent — Low-level Touch Injection

XXTouch inject touch events trực tiếp vào hệ thống qua **IOHIDEvent API**:

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Lua/JS script<br/>touch.tap(x, y)"] --> B["Coordinate Transform<br/>(orientation-aware)"]
    B --> C["IOHIDEventCreateDigitizerEvent"]
    C --> D["IOHIDEventCreateDigitizerFingerEventWithQuality"]
    D --> E["IOHIDEventAppendEvent"]
    E --> F["IOHIDEventSystemClientDispatchEvent"]
    F --> G["System HID Layer<br/>(as if real finger)"]
```

### IOHIDEvent Functions Used

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `IOHIDEventCreateDigitizerEvent` | Tạo digitizer event container |
| `IOHIDEventCreateDigitizerFingerEventWithQuality` | Tạo finger touch với pressure/quality |
| `IOHIDEventCreateKeyboardEvent` | Tạo keyboard event (key_down/key_up) |
| `IOHIDEventAppendEvent` | Gắn child event vào parent |
| `IOHIDEventSystemClientCreate` | Tạo HID system client |
| `IOHIDEventSystemClientDispatchEvent` | **Dispatch event vào hệ thống** |
| `IOHIDEventSet*Value*` | Set timestamp, flags, sender ID, float/int values |

### Touch JavaScript API

```javascript
// Coordinate transformation cho orientation
touch.tap(x, y, delayMs, waitMs)    // Tap tại tọa độ
touch.on(x, y)                      // Touch down
touch.off(x, y)                     // Touch up  
touch.move(x, y)                    // Touch move

// Multi-touch support
touch.sendMulti(events)  // Array of {x, y, ...} events

// Obj-C bridge methods
performTouchDown:channel:
performTouchMove:channel:
performTouchUp:channel:
```

> **Key insight**: Touch events được transform theo orientation trước khi dispatch — `transformCoords(evt.x, evt.y)` đảm bảo tọa độ chính xác bất kể device ở portrait hay landscape.

### Toast / Alert UI

| Component | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Toast** | `SIAlertView` bundle — custom alert library at `/var/mobile/Media/1ferver/bundles/SIAlertView.bundle/` |
| **Toast notification** | `SIToastViewDidTapNotification` — tap handler cho toast |
| **Web Toast** | `XXTUIToastWebWindow` — WKWebView-based toast window |
| **Web View** | `XXTUIWebViewController` + `XXTUIWebWindow` — full web view overlay |
| **System Alert** | `UIAlertController` / `UIAlertView` bridge |
| **Daemon UI** | `XXTUIService.app` hiển thị overlay windows khi locked |

