## 5️⃣ Scripting Runtime

### Dual Engine: Lua 5.3 + JavaScriptCore

| Engine | File | Use Case |
|---|---|---|
| **Lua 5.3** | `1feaks.dylib` (embedded) | User scripts (`.lua`, `.xxt`, `.xpa`) |
| **JavaScriptCore** | `libxxtouch.so` | Core runtime, WebRTC, screen/touch API |

**Lua module search paths**:
```
/usr/bin/1ferver/lib/?.so
/var/jb/usr/bin/1ferver/lib/?.so
/var/mobile/Media/1ferver/lib/?.so
/var/mobile/Media/1ferver/lua/?.lua
/var/mobile/Media/1ferver/lua/scripts/?.lua
```

**Native Lua modules**: `ev.so` (event loop — libev), `lpeg.so` / `lpeglabel.so` (parsing), `openssl.so`, `posix.so`, `zip.so`

