## 📊 Tổng Kết

| Feature | Technology | Maturity |
|---|---|---|
| **Daemon** | LaunchDaemon + posix_spawn + process disguise | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **WebRTC Streaming** | Native RTCPeerConnection + IOSurface + H264 HW encode | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Signaling** | JSCWebSocketServer + SRWebSocket + SDP/ICE | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Touch Simulation** | IOHIDEvent injection (system-level, bypasses sandbox) | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **OCR** | Dual: PaddleOCR (neural) + Tesseract (traditional) | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Computer Vision** | OpenCV 3.4 + Paddle-Lite ML inference | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Scripting** | Lua 5.3 (user) + JSC (runtime) dual engine | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **System Hooks** | MobileSubstrate + private frameworks | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |

> **Đây là architecture rất sophisticated** — kết hợp native WebRTC stack (không phải WebView wrapper), system-level IOHIDEvent injection, dual OCR engine (neural + traditional), và process disguise technique. Toàn bộ được bridge qua JSC runtime cho phép Lua scripts gọi high-level API (`screen.*`, `touch.*`) mà không cần biết implementation chi tiết.
